<p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.38; padding: 0pt 0pt 8pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-78616358-7fff-297f-f411-a8b1605436b6"><span style="background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">আমরা যদি</span> <span style="background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">ইন থেকে আউট</span> <span style="background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">মানে A থেকে B</span> <span style="background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">তে যাই তাহলে সকল এবং কিছু-এর </span></span><span style="font-weight: 700; white-space: pre-wrap; ">সাথে জড়িত পরিস্থিতিগুলি</span><span><span style="background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> সঠিক হবে যেমন সমস্ত A হল B এবং কিছু A হল B</span></span></p>

