&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Conclusions:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;I.&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Some pencils being balls is a possibility&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;rarr;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;F&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;ollow&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;(As s&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;ome pencils are rods&lt;/span&gt; and a&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;ll balls are rods&lt;/span&gt;. So, as no direct negative or cross relation is given between pencils&amp;nbsp;and balls&amp;nbsp;therefore it is definitely possible)&lt;/p&gt;

